This rule focuses on client-side rendering aspects for "FTBKingdoms".

**Client Setup Event (`FMLClientSetupEvent`):** Register `MenuScreens`, `EntityRenderers`, `BlockEntityRenderers`.
**Block Entity Renderers (`BlockEntityRenderer`):** Implement `render()`, register with `BlockEntityRenderers.register(ModBlockEntities.YOUR_BLOCK_ENTITY.get(), YourBER::new);`.
**Entity Renderers (`EntityRenderer`):** Register with `EntityRenderers.register(...)`. [22]
**Custom GUI Screens (`Screen`, `AbstractContainerScreen`):** Register with `MenuScreens.register(...)`.
**Model Layers (`EntityModelLayer`):** Define constants (e.g., `new ModelLayerLocation(new ResourceLocation(FTBKingdoms.MOD_ID, "example_layer"), "main")`), register definitions in `EntityRenderersEvent.RegisterLayerDefinitions`. [22]


**Consider custom renderers for "FTBKingdoms":** Treasury Block, Jail Blocks, Claim visualization overlays.